      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIt appears that every call to class_connect() is followed by class_conn2export().\n\n rc = class_connect(&conn, obd, cluuid);\n if (rc)\n         RETURN(rc);\n\n *exp = class_conn2export(&conn);\n LASSERT(exp != NULL);\n\nIs there a reason that we allocate, put, and get the export in this way? If not then let's refactor this.",
